<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Karlstejn Castle is just a 40-minute drive away from Prague and is one of the most famous Czech castles! Discover the charming village of Karlstejn with the gothic castle that sits in the forest-covered hills above. The castle was very important, as the Bohemian crown jewels used to be kept here. You can learn all about its unique history by joining a guided tour (recommended on your trip!).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Because of its position on the hill, there are amazing views out over the Czech countryside. It&#x2019;s even possible to take a walk in the luscious nature around the castle itself.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/czech-republic\/prague\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Take a day trip to Karlstejn from Prague<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134842\/Karlstjen-Castle-2.jpg\" alt=\"Castles Czech Republic\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Castles Czech Republic\" class=\"wp-image-63580 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134842\/Karlstjen-Castle-2.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134842\/Karlstjen-Castle-2-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134842\/Karls