\n\n<ul><li><strong>The Royal Palace.<\/strong> There&#x2019;s so much history to discover here, as this was home to the Czech Kings and Queens throughout the ages.<\/li><li><strong>St Vitus Cathedral.<\/strong> This building is an icon of Prague; the St Vitus twin spires can be seen for miles around.<\/li><li><strong>Golden Lane.<\/strong> Discover a medieval cobbled street lined with colorful cottages.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Prague castle is so huge that it&#x2019;s split into separate tours: A, B, and C circuit.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134933\/Prague-Castle-1-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"Castles Czech Republic\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Castles Czech Republic\" data-id=\"63590\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134933\/Prague-Castle-1.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=63590\" class=\"wp-image-63590 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134933\/Prague-Castle-1-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134933\/Prague-Castle-1-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\