dens. Don&#x2019;t forget to climb the 150 steps to the top of the tower! You&#x2019;ll experience incredible panoramic views out over the medieval town and the river below.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read more:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/czech-republic\/cesky-krumlov\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The 2-day guide to Cesky Krumlov<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134743\/cesky-krumlov-castle-6-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"Cesky Krumlov Castle\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Cesky Krumlov Castle\" data-id=\"63568\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134743\/cesky-krumlov-castle-6.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=63568\" class=\"wp-image-63568 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134743\/cesky-krumlov-castle-6-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134743\/cesky-krumlov-castle-6-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134743\/cesky-krumlov-castle-6-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/011