ng World War 2!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip: <\/strong>Visit in the fall, when the orange roof is set against the fiery reds of the surrounding woodland leaves.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/61915&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/03110619\/castles-czech-republic-1.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/03110619\/castles-czech-republic-1-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/03110619\/castles-czech-republic-1-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"9 Best Castles in the Czech Republic\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-7-pernstejn-castle-in-the-czech-republic\"><strong>7. Pernstejn Castle<\/strong> in the Czech Republic<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Pernstejn Castle really feels like the setting from a Harry Potter movie! It sits on a steep rock, high above the town below, and it&#x2019;s built at an angle that makes it look like it&#x2019;s leaning. However, these crooked walls and turrets are all part of the charm; it truly makes you feel like you&#x2019;re visiting one of the most ancient castles in the Czech Republic.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134923\/Pernstejn-Castle-2.jpg\" alt=\"Castles Czech Republic\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Castles Czech Republic\" class=\"wp-image-63588 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134923\/Pernstejn-Castle-2.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134923\/Pernstejn-Castle-2-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134923\/Pernstejn-Castle-2-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134923\/Pernstejn-Castle-2-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134923\/Pernstejn-Castle-2-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134923\/Pernstejn-Castle-2-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134923\/Pernstejn-Castle-2-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134923\/Pernstejn-Castle-2-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134923\/Pernstejn-Castle-2-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134923\/Pernstejn-Castle-2-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134923\/Pernstejn-Castle-2-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134923\/Pernstejn-Castle-2-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134923\/Pernstejn-Castle-2-600x899.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134923\/Pernstejn-Castle-2-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01134923\/Pernstejn-Castle-2.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>There are lots of tours to choose from. For example, you can even do one that takes you underground into the spooky cellars of the castle!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Did you know?<\/strong> Pernstejn Castle is known in the Czech Republic as the &#x2018;marble castle&#x2019; because of the marble stone that&#x2019;s used to frame the doorways and windows. It&#x2019;s also known for its spooky ghost stories!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/czech-republic\/czech-republic-travel-guide\/\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">See the full 2-week Czech route guide<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-8-litomysl-castle\"><strong>8. Litomysl Castle<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Discover Litomysl Castle: a white brick renaissance chateau, so beautiful that it could be a dream. This Czech Republic castle is particularly grand, with its arches, colonnades, and beautiful courtyards. It&#x2019;s no surprise that these incredible features saw Litomysl Castle named as a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/travel-blog\/best-unesco-world-heritage-sites\/\">UNESCO world heritage site<\/a> in 1999.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>As you&#x2019;d expect from a castle so palace-like, there are also stunning courtyards and English-inspired country gardens that make up part of the luxurious estate.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Make sure to check out the town of Litomysl too. It has beautiful wide avenues and impressive squares that sit around the rows of colorful townhouses.<\/p>\n\n\n             